The flag will be flown past the Padang before it makes its way around the perimeter of the island. 1 Locations 2 Red Lions’ heartland landing locations: Open field along Sengkang East Road, near Sengkang General Hospital Open field along Toh Guan Road, near Ng Teng Fong General Hospital Mobile column: Routes End points
